At ZanCruise Tours, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines the types of personal information we collect, how we use it, and the steps we take to safeguard your data.

1. Information We Collect

When you book a taxi transfer with ZanCruise Tours, we collect the following information:

Personal Identifiers: Name, email address, phone number
Booking Details: Pickup and drop-off locations, date, time, and payment information
Payment Information: Credit card details (processed securely via third-party payment processors)
Usage Information: How you use our website, including your IP address, browser type, and device information
2. How We Use Your Information

We use the information we collect for the following purposes:

To process and confirm your taxi transfer booking
To improve and personalize our services
To send you transaction updates, promotions, and relevant information about your booking
To enhance the security and functionality of our website
3. Sharing Your Information

We do not share your personal data with third parties except for:

Third-Party Service Providers: Payment processors, email providers, and other partners who help us deliver our services
Legal Compliance: In the event of a legal request, we may share information to comply with law enforcement or governmental authorities
4. Data Security

We implement robust security measures to protect your personal information. However, no method of internet transmission is entirely secure, and while we strive to protect your data, we cannot guarantee complete security.

5. Cookies and Tracking Technologies

Our website uses cookies and tracking technologies to improve user experience and analyze site traffic. You can manage your cookie preferences through your browser settings.

6. Your Rights

You have the right to:

Access, update, or delete your personal information
Opt out of promotional emails
Request that we restrict the processing of your data
To make any requests, please contact us directly at [contact@zancruisetours.com].

7. Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with the revised date.

Contact Us If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or your personal data, please reach out to us at [contact@zancruisetours.com].

